snippet.title: Slime Rancher : HOME SLIME HOME! ~ Sqaishey
snippet.description:
Next Episode: https://youtu.be/U3xQo3coR5A
SQAISHEY PLUSHIES!!!!! -  http://bit.ly/2d9ddEG
--------------------------------------------

Hello everyone and welcome to Slime Rancher with me Sqaishey Quack!
In this episode I will be playing around with my slimey friends on my very own ranch.
This game is amazing and super silly, I love it!
I hope you enjoy this video.

- Sqaishey
